request.description:
Para obtener la lista de pesos a mostrar en los menú desplegables.

Como son muchos los valores con el parámetro ListType se obtiene la Lista corta que es la por defecto o la Lista completa que se muestra solo a solicitud del usuario.

{
    "UserID": -1, /*Always send -1*/
    "Firstname":"Javier", /*required*/

    "CountryISO": "",/*optional. if don't know send empty*/
    "Country": "",/*the system does not analyze it. but i need a value to be sent. */
    "ZIPCode":"",/*optional. if don't know send empty*/
    "Measurement": "",/*the system does not analyze it. but i need a value to be sent.*/
    "SystemID": -1,/*optional, if don´t know send always -1*/

    "Password": "",/*optional, if don't know send empty and the system send one via email*/

    "DayNumber_Current": 0,/*the system does not analyze it. but i need a value to be sent.*/
    "MembershipID": -1,/*Always send -1*/
    "Membership": "",/*the system does not analyze it. but i need a value to be sent.*/
    "MonthPrice": 0.0000,/*Always send 0.0*/
    "UserStatusID": 0,/*Always send 0*/
    "UserStatus": "",/*the system does not analyze it. but i need a value to be sent.*/
    "CurrentHeight": 0.00,/*optional. If you have the user's Height when creating the profile, you send it, but it always sends 0. In order to send the weight, you must also send the SystemID (metric or imperial)*/

    "CurrentBMI": 0.00,/*Always send 0.0*/
    "HourTalkToAbby":-1/*optional, if don´t know send always -1 Military Form: 6pm => 1800*/
    }
